- `simulation/poisson.py` TeamAbilities, fit_dixon_coles. `data/elo.py` compute_elo/EloResult/seed_wc2026.
- `config.py` AppConfig with sub-configs (EloConfig, PoissonConfig, FeatureBuildConfig, TrainingConfig...) loaded from `config/default.toml`. statsmodels is NOT yet a dependency (pyproject.toml dependencies list).
- Project conventions (from CLAUDE.md + existing code): SOLID, TDD, methods <10 lines, classes <50 lines, files <500-600 lines, ruff line-length 100, mypy strict, dataclass value objects, module-level pure helpers + small class, dependency injection, deterministic seeds, no global state.

