Planning complete. Cycle 4 is decomposed into four dependency-ordered, single-session issues, all attached to the **Cycle 4 — Groll Hybrid & Baselines** milestone.

## What I did

1. **Read the briefing** (Cycle 4 — Model Training & Comparison) and **explored the codebase** — confirmed nothing for Cycle 4 exists yet, that the Cycle-3 feature frame (`FEATURE_COLUMNS` + `tournament`) is the model input contract, and that the legacy SVM/RF/NB trainer already uses `shuffle=False`.
