4. **Created the `area:models` label** (none existed for this domain), then created the issues in dependency order.

## Summary

```
Issue #12: feat: time-aware match dataset utility + Hybrid/OrderedLogit config models   [agent: python-pro]  (foundation — no deps)
Issue #13: feat: Groll-style RF/GBM goal-based hybrid model (primary predictor)         [agent: python-pro]  (depends #12)
